{"tid":1309100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講咩失唔失焦啦屌","createTime":"2019-07-12T05:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:36:46.000Z","uid":26820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"debcab3cdbf2337df42268f393b69beabaa3b732","tid":1309100,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"失乜焦呀？<br />\n我地覺得迷茫係因為個垃圾政府一路都唔撚<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">正面回應</span></strong><br />\n光復上水 18區遊行 連儂牆呢啲<br />\n係我地要喚醒更多嘅人 更多港豬企係我地呢邊<br />\n依家係用民生問題反映個政府有幾撚垃圾<br />\n再帶返去個大焦點：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求</span></span>呀！<br />\n<strong>唔撚該咪再講咩失焦！！！</strong><br />\n就係因為我地唔知做咩有用 我地先咩都要做呀！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">上水 沙田見啦！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e66a15db661ff4ece5091b4c7a92dab5c62e3a66","tid":1309100,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"5451943e4f929b95ea7c2c089129fe30dce8fa65","tid":1309100,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"b6a2da1f3ed6a2a53688cf3e8044d60a0593407e","tid":1309100,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea62b3b36c2bb87be5be538c7bf327da13517bde","tid":1309100,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c895e8eafadd012ffcd90d169b67ab92fdb0588","tid":1309100,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a97387002cb9a485d8d4a6de0f172e825e19d18","tid":1309100,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb8802136c1cebcd47f8080085f8a51948c17503","tid":1309100,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"開錯台"}]}